---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Health Disclaimer — CalorieMetric"
  description="CalorieMetric provides AI-generated calorie estimates for informational purposes only. This is not medical advice. Always consult a registered nutritionist or dietitian."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prose-page">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Health Disclaimer</h1>

      <h2>Not medical advice</h2>
      <p>
        The information provided by CalorieMetric — including calorie calculations, meal estimates, and nutritional guidance — is intended for general informational and educational purposes only. It is <strong>not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</strong>
      </p>

      <h2>AI-generated estimates</h2>
      <p>
        Calorie estimates for logged meals are generated by an AI language model (Groq / Llama). These are approximations only. Actual calorie content can vary significantly based on preparation methods, ingredient brands, portion sizes, and individual metabolism. The estimates should not be relied upon for medical, clinical, or therapeutic nutrition planning.
      </p>

      <h2>Consult a professional</h2>
      <p>
        Always consult a qualified healthcare provider, registered dietitian, or certified nutritionist before making significant changes to your diet, especially if you have or suspect any medical condition including but not limited to diabetes, eating disorders, cardiovascular disease, or kidney disease.
      </p>

      <h2>Individual variation</h2>
      <p>
        Calorie needs vary significantly between individuals based on genetics, health status, medications, and other factors. The Mifflin-St Jeor formula provides a scientific estimate, but it is still an estimate. Results may vary.
      </p>

      <h2>No liability</h2>
      <p>
        CalorieMetric and its operators accept no liability for decisions made based on information provided by this tool. Use of CalorieMetric is at your own risk.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@caloriemetric.com" style="color: var(--color-accent-deep); text-decoration: underline;">hello@caloriemetric.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
